channel.title: ~~~ so long ~~ Intrested users read? ~~~
channel.description:
to begin this is 'the' last message I'll place on moparscape pserver section. I thought I did put the last message in my client development thread but as soon as I found out the development leader of the game we were going to create first had to go to america for some business I was back to these forums to chissel of some time because I didn't really had something to do unless practice some with graphics. Now I have a fulltime job as GFX'er and I don't really have to chissel of time.
I also gave some reputation to some persons that where good in the time I knew them, or persons that I appriciated. So mods don't have to take the reputation of those persons thinking I was abusing the Rep system. my total time logged in was: 16 days, 6 hours and 3 minutes in the past year and a half. I might be breaking a rule by posting this in 2 different sections but I don't care what I get (mute, warned, whatever) but I do not leave spamming.
So long.
